### tryParseScalarRegister {#a4f4606aeef233010982ced4c68c17709}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype={<>ParseStatus AArch64AsmParser::tryParseScalarRegister (<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/mcregister">MCRegister</a> &amp; RegNum)</>}>
&#125;
